Package org.dmsextension.paperless.client.endpoints

Klasse SingleDocumentEndpoint

java.lang.Object
org.dmsextension.paperless.client.endpoints.PaperlessEndpoint
org.dmsextension.paperless.client.endpoints.ParameterEndpoint
org.dmsextension.paperless.client.endpoints.SingleDocumentEndpoint
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
IEndpoint, IParametrizedEndpoint
public class SingleDocumentEndpoint extends ParameterEndpoint implements IParametrizedEndpoint
Endpoint for single documents. Endpoint: "/documents/{{id}}/

Needed path parameters
Param Description
id ID of the document in paperless

Possible query elements
Element Type Description Example
fields array Custom fields the endpoint should return ["Invoice Number","Date"]

Methods
Method Used for
GET Retrieving document with given id
DELETE Delete the document with given id
PATCH Update given document. Only updates given entries, everything else stays the same
PUT Updates given document. Overwrites entire entry of document, earlier information is lost.
